  "_comment": "Foreign Battlefield Plains (外域战场平原) — the vast war-scarred battle plains of the Foreign Battleground dimension. Canon: an endless, arid battlefield where cultivators from cultivation planets clash for their planet's survival and ranking. The sky is blood-tinged, spirit energy is dense but chaotic, and the ground is littered with the corpses of fallen cultivators, shattered weapons, and the resentment that fuels soul storms. Beached shipwrecks serve as stand-ins for the broken war engines and corpse-piles of the fallen. Witherskeletons stand in for the vengeful spirits of fallen cultivators. Horses remain as remnants of war mounts. Prime Directive: the war was objectively fought here — the corpses, the chaotic energy, and the blood-tinged sky are real regardless of the player's perception or cultivation level.",
